formatDescription: The Netscape Bookmark File Format was originally created to store bookmarks for the Netscape web browser. It was subsequently used by Internet Explorer. Microsoft have provided a thorough description of the format: https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/previous-versions/windows/internet-explorer/ie-developer/platform-apis/aa753582(v=vs.85)
